For Rest of the open-unlearning documentation refer to the original repository.

clone this repo with `--recursive`


For running our eval experiments on WMDP dataset:

```
bash eval.sh {method} {unlearning_task}
```

method -> ga or rmu 

unlearning_task -> bio or cyber



`tofu_rome.py` for applying ROME/r-ROME knowledge edit methods on TOFU dataset

